Class IloCplex.CalcQCPDuals

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.CalcQCPDuals
  • Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.CalcQCPDuals
extends java.lang.Object

    Enumeration of possible values for the QCP dual computation parameter IloCplex.IntParam.CalcQCPDuals.

    Use these values with the method IloCplex.setParam like this: setParam(IloCplex.CalcQCPDuals, value).
